                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310407-71-victim675 t18310407-71-viclabel404"></join>. On Monday morning, the 14th of March, I went out about ten o'clock - I returned a little before eleven, and missed a picture which had hang up in my shop, within reach of my door - I have one window taken out, and a person on the step of the private door might reach to where this picture had hung.</p>

