               <p>Prisoner. I never pawned that picture with you. Witness. Yes, you did.</p>
               <p>COURT. Q. Are you quite sure you saw him? A. Yes - he was five or ten minutes in the shop; I was writing the duplicates - I have the counterpart of the duplicate; I had not seen him before.</p>
